text: Manita Devkota (born 1995) in Gorkha Nepal is a Nepali Model & beauty pageant titleholder of Miss Universe Nepal 2018. She defeated 25 participants in the Miss Nepal pageant which was held on 11th April 2018. She is 2nd Miss Nepal Universe of the Nation crowned by 1st Miss Universe Nepal, Nagma Shrestha. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1996 births Category:Nepalese models Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners
